      cat lacrosse.txt >> tennis.txt.       Append the contents 
      cat < gymnastics.txt                 redirect the contents as standard input 

      cat lacrosse.txt | wc.       wordcount command.

cat lakes.txt | sort
cat lakes.txt | sort > sorted-lakes.txt 

sort deserts.txt | uniq     command to filter out adjacent, duplicate lines



grep -i Mount mountains.txt.            without case sensitivity.

grep -R Island          filenames and lines with matching results.
